To change your default font in windows:

* find out the name of the font you want to change to by selecting the font.
  press S-Mouse1 and choose the font you desire.
* copy the name of this font into a buffer somewhere
  M-x describe-face RET RET
  select the face name, eg: outline-bitstream vera sans mono and M-w to copy to the kill ring
* customise the default-face
  M-x customize-face RET default RET
  edit Font Family: and yank the font name from the kill buffer C-y
* click the safe for future sessions, and then click finish.

